name: JP style News Anchor on TV (horizontal/portrait)
description:
Hi I am Yamada San, I publish LoRA and models regularly.

More photo on discord and twitter! Please follow me if you like!

https://twitter.com/yamada_artist

https://discord.com/invite/NfXu9QDX96

This funny loRA is specific to generate JP style news anchor
You can also set the generation size to 768 x 512 px.

This model is hard to be trained and plz expect generation successful rate is around 50%.

They are just illustration and not real news anchor of any companies and organizations.

For testing and study purpose only.

This loRA is not depicting any specific persons or any organizations. It provides only the style and random outlook.
